                                            })]
                                        })]
                                    }), e.jsx(Ca, {}), e.jsxs("div", {
                                        className: "space-y-2",
                                        children: [e.jsx(q, {
                                            children: "Tiempo límite de importación"
                                        }), e.jsxs(He, {
                                            defaultValue: "3600",
                                            children: [e.jsx(Ue, {
                                                children: e.jsx(We, {})
                                            }), e.jsxs(qe, {
                                                children: [e.jsx(Q, {
                                                    value: "1800",
                                                    children: "30 minutos"
                                                }), e.jsx(Q, {
                                                    value: "3600",
                                                    children: "1 hora"
                                                }), e.jsx(Q, {
                                                    value: "7200",
                                                    children: "2 horas"
                                                }), e.jsx(Q, {
                                                    value: "14400",
                                                    children: "4 horas"
                                                })]
                                            })]
                                        })]
                                    })]
                                })]
                            }), e.jsxs(V, {
                                children: [e.jsx(ae, {
                                    children: e.jsxs("div", {
                                        className: "flex justify-between items-center",
                                        children: [e.jsx(ie, {
                                            children: "Estadísticas Generales"
                                        }), e.jsxs(M, {
                                            size: "sm",
                                            variant: "outline",
                                            onClick: ge,
                                            className: "text-orange-600 hover:text-orange-700",
                                            children: [e.jsx(Jt, {
                                                className: "h-3 w-3 mr-1"
                                            }), "Limpiar Estadísticas"]
                                        })]
                                    })
                                }), e.jsx(U, {
                                    children: R && e.jsxs("div", {
                                        className: "space-y-4",
                                        children: [e.jsxs("div", {
                                            className: "grid grid-cols-2 gap-4",
                                            children: [e.jsxs("div", {
                                                className: "text-center",
                                                children: [e.jsx("p", {
                                                    className: "text-2xl font-bold",
                                                    children: R.totalImports || 0
                                                }), e.jsx("p", {
                                                    className: "text-sm text-muted-foreground",
                                                    children: "Importaciones totales"
                                                })]
                                            }), e.jsxs("div", {
                                                className: "text-center",
                                                children: [e.jsxs("p", {
                                                    className: "text-2xl font-bold",
                                                    children: [R.successRate || 0, "%"]
                                                }), e.jsx("p", {
                                                    className: "text-sm text-muted-foreground",
                                                    children: "Tasa de éxito"
                                                })]
                                            })]
                                        }), e.jsx(Ca, {}), e.jsxs("div", {
                                            className: "space-y-2",
                                            children: [e.jsxs("p", {
                                                className: "text-sm",
                                                children: [e.jsx("span", {
                                                    className: "font-medium",
                                                    children: "Última importación:"
                                                }), " ", R.lastImport ? new Date(R.lastImport).toLocaleString() : "Nunca"]
                                            }), e.jsxs("p", {
                                                className: "text-sm",
                                                children: [e.jsx("span", {
                                                    className: "font-medium",
                                                    children: "Próxima programada:"
                                                }), " ", R.nextScheduled ? new Date(R.nextScheduled).toLocaleString() : "No programada"]
                                            })]
                                        })]
                                    })
                                })]
                            })]
                        })
                    })]
                })]
            })]
        })
    };
function VM({content: t, onChange: s, placeholder: r, className: n}) {
    const a = h.useRef(null),
        [i, o] = h.useState(!1),
        [l, c] = h.useState(t);
    h.useEffect(() => {
        if (c(t), a.current && a.current.innerHTML !== t) {
            const p = ui.sanitize(t, {
                ALLOWED_TAGS: ["p", "br", "strong", "em", "u", "h1", "h2", "h3", "h4", "h5", "h6", "ul", "ol", "li", "a", "img", "div"],
                ALLOWED_ATTR: ["href", "target", "rel", "src", "alt", "style", "class"],
                ALLOWED_URI_REGEXP: /^(?:(?:(?:f|ht)tps?|mailto|tel|callto|cid|xmpp|data):|[^a-z]|[a-z+.\-]+(?:[^a-z+.\-:]|$))/i
            });
            a.current.innerHTML = p
        }
    }, [t]);
    const d = () => {
            if (a.current) {
                const p = a.current.innerHTML;
                c(p),
                s(p)
            }
        },
        u = p => {
            if (c(p), s(p), a.current) {
                const v = ui.sanitize(p, {
                    ALLOWED_TAGS: ["p", "br", "strong", "em", "u", "h1", "h2", "h3", "h4", "h5", "h6", "ul", "ol", "li", "a", "img", "div"],
                    ALLOWED_ATTR: ["href", "target", "rel", "src", "alt", "style", "class"],
                    ALLOWED_URI_REGEXP: /^(?:(?:(?:f|ht)tps?|mailto|tel|callto|cid|xmpp|data):|[^a-z]|[a-z+.\-]+(?:[^a-z+.\-:]|$))/i
                });
                a.current.innerHTML = v
            }
        },
        m = (p, v) => {
            var N;
            try {
                document.queryCommandSupported && document.queryCommandSupported(p) ? document.execCommand(p, !1, v) : f(p, v)
            } catch (w) {
                console.warn("Error executing command:", p, w),
                f(p, v)
            }
            (N = a.current) == null || N.focus(),
            d()
        },
        f = (p, v) => {
            if (!a.current)
                return;
            const N = window.getSelection();
            if (!N || N.rangeCount === 0)
                return;
            const w = N.getRangeAt(0);
            switch (p) {
            case "bold":
                y("strong");
                break;
            case "italic":
                y("em");
                break;
            case "underline":
                y("u");
                break;
            case "createLink":
                if (v) {
                    const C = document.createElement("a");
                    C.href = v,
                    C.target = "_blank",
                    C.rel = "noopener noreferrer";
                    try {
                        w.surroundContents(C)
                    } catch {
                        w.deleteContents(),
                        w.insertNode(C)
                    }
                }
                break;
            case "insertImage":
                if (v) {
                    const C = document.createElement("img");
                    C.src = v,
                    C.style.maxWidth = "100%",
                    C.style.height = "auto",
                    w.insertNode(C)
                }
                break;
            case "insertUnorderedList":
                g("ul");
                break;
            default:
                if (p.startsWith("justify")) {
                    const C = p.replace("justify", "").toLowerCase(),
                        E = document.createElement("div");
                    E.style.textAlign = C === "left" ? "left" : C === "center" ? "center" : "right";
                    try {
                        w.surroundContents(E)
                    } catch {
                        w.deleteContents(),
                        w.insertNode(E)
                    }
                }
                break
            }
        },
        y = p => {
            const v = window.getSelection();
            if (!v || v.rangeCount === 0)
                return;
            const N = v.getRangeAt(0),
                w = N.toString();
            if (w) {
                const C = document.createElement(p);
                C.textContent = w,
                N.deleteContents(),
                N.insertNode(C)
            }
        },
        g = p => {
            const v = window.getSelection();
            if (!v || v.rangeCount === 0)
                return;
            const N = v.getRangeAt(0),
                w = N.toString();
            if (w) {
                const C = document.createElement(p),
                    E = document.createElement("li");
                E.textContent = w,
                C.appendChild(E),
                N.deleteContents(),
                N.insertNode(C)
            }
        },
        x = () => {
            const p = prompt("Ingrese la URL:");
            p && m("createLink", p)
        },
        j = () => {
            const p = prompt("Ingrese la URL de la imagen:");
            p && m("insertImage", p)
        },
        b = [{
            icon: o5,
            command: "bold",
            title: "Negrita"
        }, {
            icon: N5,
            command: "italic",
            title: "Cursiva"
        }, {
            icon: O5,
            command: "underline",
            title: "Subrayado"
        }, {
            icon: r5,
            command: "justifyLeft",
            title: "Alinear izquierda"
        }, {
            icon: s5,
            command: "justifyCenter",
            title: "Centrar"
        }, {
            icon: n5,
            command: "justifyRight",
            title: "Alinear derecha"
        }, {
            icon: bp,
            command: "insertUnorderedList",
            title: "Lista"
        }];
    return e.jsx("div", {
        className: ue("border rounded-lg overflow-hidden", n),
        children: e.jsxs(ls, {
            defaultValue: "visual",
            className: "w-full",
            children: [e.jsxs(es, {
                className: "grid w-full grid-cols-2",
                children: [e.jsx(Ve, {
                    value: "visual",
                    children: "Editor Visual"
                }), e.jsx(Ve, {
                    value: "html",
                    children: "Código HTML"
                })]
            }), e.jsxs(ze, {
                value: "visual",
                className: "m-0",
                children: [e.jsxs("div", {
                    className: "border-b bg-gray-50 p-2 flex flex-wrap gap-1",
                    children: [b.map(p => e.jsx(M, {
                        variant: "ghost",
                        size: "sm",
                        className: "h-8 w-8 p-0",
                        onClick: () => m(p.command),
                        title: p.title,
                        type: "button",
                        children: e.jsx(p.icon, {
                            className: "h-4 w-4"
                        })
                    }, p.command)), e.jsx("div", {
                        className: "w-px h-6 bg-gray-300 mx-1"
                    }), e.jsx(M, {
                        variant: "ghost",
                        size: "sm",
                        className: "h-8 w-8 p-0",
                        onClick: x,
                        title: "Insertar enlace",
                        type: "button",
                        children: e.jsx(C5, {
                            className: "h-4 w-4"
                        })
                    }), e.jsx(M, {
                        variant: "ghost",
                        size: "sm",
                        className: "h-8 w-8 p-0",
                        onClick: j,
                        title: "Insertar imagen",
                        type: "button",
                        children: e.jsx(Us, {
                            className: "h-4 w-4"
                        })
                    }), e.jsx("div", {
                        className: "w-px h-6 bg-gray-300 mx-1"
                    }), e.jsxs("select", {
                        onChange: p => m("formatBlock", p.target.value),
                        className: "h-8 px-2 text-sm border rounded",
                        defaultValue: "",
                        children: [e.jsx("option", {
                            value: "",
                            children: "Formato"
                        }), e.jsx("option", {
                            value: "h1",
                            children: "Título 1"
                        }), e.jsx("option", {
                            value: "h2",
                            children: "Título 2"
                        }), e.jsx("option", {
                            value: "h3",
                            children: "Título 3"
                        }), e.jsx("option", {
                            value: "p",
                            children: "Párrafo"
                        })]
                    })]
                }), e.jsxs("div", {
                    className: "relative",
                    children: [e.jsx("div", {
                        ref: a,
                        contentEditable: !0,
                        onInput: d,
                        onFocus: () => o(!0),
                        onBlur: () => o(!1),
                        className: ue("min-h-[300px] p-4 outline-none prose prose-sm max-w-none", "focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-500 focus:ring-inset", !t && !i && "text-gray-400"),
                        style: {
                            whiteSpace: "pre-wrap",
                            wordWrap: "break-word"
                        },
                        suppressContentEditableWarning: !0
                    }), !t && !i && e.jsx("div", {
                        className: "absolute top-4 left-4 text-gray-400 pointer-events-none",
                        children: r || "Escriba el contenido aquí..."
                    })]
                })]
            }), e.jsx(ze, {
                value: "html",
                className: "m-0",
                children: e.jsx(Ut, {
                    value: l,
                    onChange: p => u(p.target.value),
                    placeholder: "Ingrese el código HTML aquí...",
                    className: "min-h-[400px] font-mono text-sm border-0 rounded-none resize-none"
                })
            })]
        })
    })
}
function eY() {
    const [t, s] = h.useState("pages"),
        [r, n] = h.useState(null),
        [a, i] = h.useState(null),
        [o, l] = h.useState({}),
        [c, d] = h.useState({}),
        [u, m] = h.useState(!1),
        [f, y] = h.useState(!1),
        {toast: g} = tt(),
        x = hr(),
        {data: j, isLoading: b} = _e({
            queryKey: ["/api/admin/cms/pages"],
            queryFn: async () => {
                const R = await fetch("/api/admin/cms/pages", {
                    credentials: "include"
                });
                if (!R.ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al cargar páginas");
                return R.json()
            }
        }),
        {data: p, isLoading: v} = _e({
            queryKey: ["/api/admin/cms/footer-blocks"],
            queryFn: async () => {
                const R = await fetch("/api/admin/cms/footer-blocks", {
                    credentials: "include"
                });
                if (!R.ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al cargar bloques");
                return R.json()
            }
        }),
        {data: N, isLoading: w, error: C} = _e({
            queryKey: ["/api/cms/site-settings"],
            queryFn: async () => {
                const R = await fetch("/api/cms/site-settings", {
                    credentials: "include"
                });
                if (!R.ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al cargar configuraciones");
                return R.json()
            }
        }),
        E = async () => {
            try {
                const R = r ? "PUT" : "POST",
                    z = r ? `/api/admin/cms/pages/${r.id}` : "/api/admin/cms/pages";
                if (!(await fetch(z, {
                    method: R,
                    headers: {
                        "Content-Type": "application/json"
                    },
                    credentials: "include",
                    body: JSON.stringify(o)
                })).ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al guardar página");
                x.invalidateQueries({
                    queryKey: ["/api/admin/cms/pages"]
                }),
                n(null),
                l({}),
                m(!1),
                g({
                    title: r ? "Página actualizada exitosamente" : "Página creada exitosamente"
                })
            } catch {
                g({
                    title: "Error al guardar página",
                    variant: "destructive"
                })
            }
        },
        k = async R => {
            try {
                if (!(await fetch(`/api/admin/cms/pages/${R}`, {
                    method: "DELETE",
                    credentials: "include"
                })).ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al eliminar página");
                x.invalidateQueries({
                    queryKey: ["/api/admin/cms/pages"]
                }),
                g({
                    title: "Página eliminada exitosamente"
                })
            } catch {
                g({
                    title: "Error al eliminar página",
                    variant: "destructive"
                })
            }
        },
        D = async () => {
            try {
                const R = a ? "PUT" : "POST",
                    z = a ? `/api/admin/cms/footer-blocks/${a.id}` : "/api/admin/cms/footer-blocks";
                if (!(await fetch(z, {
                    method: R,
                    headers: {
                        "Content-Type": "application/json"
                    },
                    credentials: "include",
                    body: JSON.stringify(c)
                })).ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al guardar bloque");
                x.invalidateQueries({
                    queryKey: ["/api/admin/cms/footer-blocks"]
                }),
                i(null),
                d({}),
                y(!1),
                g({
                    title: a ? "Bloque actualizado exitosamente" : "Bloque creado exitosamente"
                })
            } catch {
                g({
                    title: "Error al guardar bloque",
                    variant: "destructive"
                })
            }
        },
        K = async R => {
            try {
                if (!(await fetch(`/api/admin/cms/footer-blocks/${R}`, {
                    method: "DELETE",
                    credentials: "include"
                })).ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al eliminar bloque");
                x.invalidateQueries({
                    queryKey: ["/api/admin/cms/footer-blocks"]
                }),
                g({
                    title: "Bloque eliminado exitosamente"
                })
            } catch {
                g({
                    title: "Error al eliminar bloque",
                    variant: "destructive"
                })
            }
        },
        L = async (R, z) => {
            try {
                if (!(await fetch(`/api/cms/site-settings/${R}`, {
                    method: "PUT",
                    headers: {
                        "Content-Type": "application/json"
                    },
                    credentials: "include",
                    body: JSON.stringify({
                        value: z
                    })
                })).ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al actualizar configuración");
                x.invalidateQueries({
                    queryKey: ["/api/cms/site-settings"]
                }),
                g({
                    title: "Configuración actualizada exitosamente"
                })
            } catch {
                g({
                    title: "Error al actualizar configuración",
                    variant: "destructive"
                })
            }
        };
    return e.jsxs("div", {
        className: "flex min-h-screen bg-background",
        children: [e.jsx(zs, {
            activeTab: "admin_cms"
        }), e.jsxs("div", {
            className: "flex-1 p-6",
            children: [e.jsx("h1", {
                className: "text-3xl font-bold mb-8",
                children: "Sistema de Gestión de Contenido"
            }), e.jsxs("div", {
                className: "flex space-x-2 mb-6 border-b pb-4",
                children: [e.jsx(M, {
                    variant: t === "pages" ? "default" : "outline",
                    onClick: () => s("pages"),
                    children: "Páginas"
                }), e.jsx(M, {
                    variant: t === "footer" ? "default" : "outline",
                    onClick: () => s("footer"),
                    children: "Footer"
                }), e.jsx(M, {
                    variant: t === "settings" ? "default" : "outline",
                    onClick: () => s("settings"),
                    children: "Configuraciones"
                })]
            }), t === "pages" && e.jsxs("div", {
                className: "space-y-6",
                children: [e.jsxs("div", {
                    className: "flex justify-between items-center",
                    children: [e.jsx("h2", {
                        className: "text-2xl font-semibold",
                        children: "Gestión de Páginas"
                    }), e.jsxs(M, {
                        onClick: () => {
                            m(!0),
                            l({
                                title: "",
                                slug: "",
                                content: "",
                                metaDescription: "",
                                isPublished: !0,
                                isEditable: !0,
                                pageType: "static"
                            })
                        },
                        children: [e.jsx(on, {
                            className: "w-4 h-4 mr-2"
                        }), "Nueva Página"]
                    })]
                }), e.jsxs("div", {
                    className: "grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-6",
                    children: [e.jsxs(V, {
                        children: [e.jsx(ae, {
                            children: e.jsx(ie, {
                                children: "Páginas Existentes"
                            })
                        }), e.jsx(U, {
                            className: "space-y-4",
                            children: b ? e.jsx("div", {
                                children: "Cargando páginas..."
                            }) : j == null ? void 0 : j.map(R => e.jsxs("div", {
                                className: "flex items-center justify-between p-4 border rounded-lg",
                                children: [e.jsxs("div", {
                                    className: "space-y-1",
                                    children: [e.jsx("h3", {
                                        className: "font-medium",
                                        children: R.title
                                    }), e.jsxs("p", {
                                        className: "text-sm text-muted-foreground",
                                        children: ["/", R.slug]
                                    }), e.jsxs("div", {
                                        className: "flex gap-2",
                                        children: [e.jsx(ve, {
                                            variant: R.isPublished ? "default" : "secondary",
                                            children: R.isPublished ? "Publicada" : "Borrador"
                                        }), e.jsx(ve, {
                                            variant: "outline",
                                            children: R.pageType
                                        })]
                                    })]
                                }), e.jsxs("div", {
                                    className: "flex gap-2",
                                    children: [e.jsx(M, {
                                        size: "sm",
                                        variant: "outline",
                                        onClick: () => {
                                            n(R),
                                            l(R),
                                            m(!1)
                                        },
                                        children: e.jsx(Br, {
                                            className: "w-4 h-4"
                                        })
                                    }), R.isEditable && e.jsx(M, {
                                        size: "sm",
                                        variant: "destructive",
                                        onClick: () => k(R.id),
                                        children: e.jsx(Jt, {
                                            className: "w-4 h-4"
                                        })
                                    })]
                                })]
                            }, R.id))
                        })]
                    }), (r || u) && e.jsxs(V, {
                        children: [e.jsx(ae, {
                            children: e.jsx(ie, {
                                children: u ? "Nueva Página" : `Editando: ${r == null ? void 0 : r.title}`
                            })
                        }), e.jsxs(U, {
                            className: "space-y-4",
                            children: [e.jsxs("div", {
                                className: "space-y-2",
                                children: [e.jsx(q, {
                                    htmlFor: "title",
                                    children: "Título"
                                }), e.jsx(se, {
                                    id: "title",
                                    value: o.title || "",
                                    onChange: R => l({
                                        ...o,
                                        title: R.target.value
                                    }),
                                    placeholder: "Título de la página"
                                })]
                            }), e.jsxs("div", {
                                className: "space-y-2",
                                children: [e.jsx(q, {
                                    htmlFor: "slug",
                                    children: "Slug (URL)"
                                }), e.jsx(se, {
                                    id: "slug",
                                    value: o.slug || "",
                                    onChange: R => l({
                                        ...o,
                                        slug: R.target.value
                                    }),
                                    placeholder: "url-de-la-pagina"
                                })]
                            }), e.jsxs("div", {
                                className: "space-y-2",
                                children: [e.jsx(q, {
                                    htmlFor: "content",
                                    children: "Contenido"
                                }), e.jsx(VM, {
                                    content: o.content || "",
                                    onChange: R => l({
                                        ...o,
                                        content: R
                                    }),
                                    placeholder: "Escriba el contenido de la página aquí...",
                                    className: "min-h-[400px]"
                                })]
                            }), e.jsxs("div", {
                                className: "flex items-center space-x-2",
                                children: [e.jsx(St, {
                                    id: "isPublished",
                                    checked: o.isPublished || !1,
                                    onCheckedChange: R => l({
                                        ...o,
                                        isPublished: R
                                    })
                                }), e.jsx(q, {
                                    htmlFor: "isPublished",
                                    children: "Página publicada"
                                })]
                            }), e.jsxs("div", {
                                className: "flex gap-2",
                                children: [e.jsxs(M, {
                                    onClick: E,
                                    children: [e.jsx(wn, {
                                        className: "w-4 h-4 mr-2"
                                    }), "Guardar"]
                                }), e.jsxs(M, {
                                    variant: "outline",
                                    onClick: () => {
                                        n(null),
                                        l({}),
                                        m(!1)
                                    },
                                    children: [e.jsx(er, {
                                        className: "w-4 h-4 mr-2"
                                    }), "Cancelar"]
                                })]
                            })]
                        })]
                    })]
                })]
            }), t === "footer" && e.jsxs("div", {
                className: "space-y-6",
                children: [e.jsxs("div", {
                    className: "flex justify-between items-center",
                    children: [e.jsx("h2", {
                        className: "text-2xl font-semibold",
                        children: "Gestión del Footer"
                    }), e.jsxs(M, {
                        onClick: () => {
                            y(!0),
                            d({
                                title: "",
                                content: "",

                            })
                        },

                            })

function tY() {
    const [, t] = dt(),
        [s, r] = h.useState(null),
        [n, a] = h.useState(""),
        [i, o] = h.useState(!1),
        l = () => {
            if (!s)
                return;
            if (o(!0), s.formHtml) {
                const f = document.createElement("div"),
                    x = new DOMParser().parseFromString(s.formHtml, "text/html").querySelector("form");
                x && f.appendChild(x.cloneNode(!0));
                const j = f.querySelector("form");
                if (j) {
                    j.style.display = "none",
                    document.body.appendChild(j),
                    j.querySelector('input[name="Ds_SignatureVersion"]'),
                    j.querySelector('input[name="Ds_MerchantParameters"]'),
                    j.querySelector('input[name="Ds_Signature"]'),
                    j.submit(),
                    sessionStorage.removeItem("redsysPaymentData");
                    return
                }
            }
            const c = document.createElement("form");
            c.method = "POST",
            c.action = s.actionUrl,
            c.acceptCharset = "UTF-8",
            c.enctype = "application/x-www-form-urlencoded",
            c.style.display = "none";
            const d = document.createElement("input");
            d.type = "hidden",
            d.name = "Ds_SignatureVersion",
            d.value = "HMAC_SHA256_V1",
            c.appendChild(d);
            const u = document.createElement("input");
            u.type = "hidden",
            u.name = "Ds_MerchantParameters",
            u.value = s.merchantParameters,
            c.appendChild(u);
            const m = document.createElement("input");
            m.type = "hidden",
            m.name = "Ds_Signature",
            m.value = s.signature,
            c.appendChild(m),
            document.body.appendChild(c),
            c.submit(),
            sessionStorage.removeItem("redsysPaymentData")
        };
    return h.useEffect(() => {
        const c = sessionStorage.getItem("redsysPaymentData");
        if (!c) {
            a("No se encontraron datos de pago. Redirigiendo al checkout..."),
            setTimeout(() => t("/checkout"), 3e3);
            return
        }
        try {
            const d = JSON.parse(c);
            r(d),
            setTimeout(() => {
                l()
            }, 1500)
        } catch {
            a("Error al procesar los datos de pago")
        }
    }, [t]), n ? e.jsx("div", {
        className: "min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-50",
        children: e.jsx("div", {
            className: "max-w-md w-full bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6",
            children: e.jsxs("div", {
                className: "text-center",
                children: [e.jsx("div", {
                    className: "w-12 h-12 mx-auto mb-4 bg-red-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center",
                    children: e.jsx("svg", {
                        className: "w-6 h-6 text-red-600",
                        fill: "none",
                        stroke: "currentColor",
                        viewBox: "0 0 24 24",
                        children: e.jsx("path", {
                            strokeLinecap: "round",
                            strokeLinejoin: "round",
                            strokeWidth: 2,
                            d: "M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-2.5L13.732 4c-.77-.833-1.964-.833-2.732 0L3.082 16.5c-.77.833.192 2.5 1.732 2.5z"
                        })
                    })
                }), e.jsx("h2", {
                    className: "text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2",
                    children: "Error en el proceso de pago"
                }), e.jsx("p", {
                    className: "text-gray-600 mb-4",
                    children: n
                }), e.jsx("button", {
                    onClick: () => t("/checkout"),
                    className: "w-full bg-blue-600 text-white py-2 px-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors",
                    children: "Volver al checkout"
                })]
            })
        })
    }) : s ? e.jsx("div", {
        className: "min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-50",
        children: e.jsx("div", {
            className: "max-w-md w-full bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6",
            children: e.jsxs("div", {
                className: "text-center",
                children: [e.jsx("div", {
                    className: "w-12 h-12 mx-auto mb-4 bg-blue-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center",
                    children: e.jsx("svg", {
                        className: "w-6 h-6 text-blue-600",
                        fill: "none",
                        stroke: "currentColor",
                        viewBox: "0 0 24 24",
                        children: e.jsx("path", {
                            strokeLinecap: "round",
                            strokeLinejoin: "round",
                            strokeWidth: 2,
                            d: "M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"
                        })
                    })
                }), e.jsx("h2", {
                    className: "text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2",
                    children: "Redirigiendo al pago seguro"
                }), e.jsx("p", {
                    className: "text-gray-600 mb-4",
                    children: "Estás siendo redirigido a la pasarela de pago segura de Redsys para completar tu compra."
                }), e.jsx("div", {
                    className: "bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 mb-6",
                    children: e.jsxs("div", {
                        className: "text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2",
                        children: [e.jsxs("div", {
                            className: "flex justify-between",
                            children: [e.jsx("span", {
                                children: "Pedido:"
                            }), e.jsx("span", {
                                className: "font-medium",
                                children: s.reference || s.orderNumber || "N/A"
                            })]
                        }), e.jsxs("div", {
                            className: "flex justify-between",
                            children: [e.jsx("span", {
                                children: "Importe:"
                            }), e.jsxs("span", {
                                className: "font-medium",
                                children: [s.totalAmount ? s.totalAmount.toFixed(2) : s.amount ? (s.amount / 100).toFixed(2) : "0.00", "€"]
                            })]
                        })]
                    })
                }), i ? e.jsx("div", {
                    className: "w-full bg-green-600 text-white py-3 px-4 rounded-lg font-medium",
                    children: e.jsxs("div", {
                        className: "flex items-center justify-center",
                        children: [e.jsx("div", {
                            className: "animate-spin rounded-full h-4 w-4 border-b-2 border-white mr-2"
                        }), "Redirigiendo a Redsys..."]
                    })
                }) : e.jsx("button", {
                    onClick: l,
                    className: "w-full bg-red-600 text-white py-3 px-4 rounded-lg hover:bg-red-700 transition-colors font-medium",
                    children: "Continuar con el pago en Redsys"
                }), e.jsx("p", {
                    className: "text-xs text-gray-500 mt-4",
                    children: "Si no eres redirigido automáticamente, haz clic en el botón de arriba."
                })]
            })
        })
    }) : e.jsx("div", {
        className: "min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center bg-gray-50",
        children: e.jsxs("div", {
            className: "text-center",
            children: [e.jsx("div", {
                className: "animate-spin rounded-full h-12 w-12 border-b-2 border-blue-600 mx-auto mb-4"
            }), e.jsx("p", {
                className: "text-gray-600",
                children: "Preparando el pago..."
            })]
        })
    })
}
function sY() {
    const [t, s] = h.useState("pages"),
        [r, n] = h.useState(null),
        [a, i] = h.useState(null),
        [o, l] = h.useState({}),
        [c, d] = h.useState({}),
        [u, m] = h.useState(!1),
        [f, y] = h.useState(!1),
        [g, x] = h.useState({}),
        [j, b] = h.useState({}),
        {toast: p} = tt(),
        v = hr(),
        {data: N, isLoading: w} = _e({
            queryKey: ["/api/admin/cms/pages"],
            queryFn: async () => {
                const A = await fetch("/api/admin/cms/pages", {
                    credentials: "include"
                });
                if (!A.ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al cargar páginas");
                return A.json()
            }
        }),
        {data: C, isLoading: E} = _e({
            queryKey: ["/api/admin/cms/footer-blocks"],
            queryFn: async () => {
                const A = await fetch("/api/admin/cms/footer-blocks", {
                    credentials: "include"
                });
                if (!A.ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al cargar bloques");
                return A.json()
            }
        }),
        {data: k, isLoading: D} = _e({
            queryKey: ["/api/cms/site-settings"],
            queryFn: async () => {
                const A = await fetch("/api/cms/site-settings", {
                    credentials: "include"
                });
                if (!A.ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al cargar configuraciones");
                return A.json()
            }
        }),
        K = async (A, P) => {
            x(I => ({
                ...I,
                [A]: !0
            }));
            try {
                if (!(await fetch(`/api/cms/site-settings/${A}`, {
                    method: "PUT",
                    headers: {
                        "Content-Type": "application/json"
                    },
                    credentials: "include",
                    body: JSON.stringify({
                        value: P
                    })
                })).ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al actualizar configuración");
                v.invalidateQueries({
                    queryKey: ["/api/cms/site-settings"]
                }),
                b($ => {
                    const ne = {
                        ...$
                    };
                    return delete ne[A], ne
                }),
                p({
                    title: "Configuración guardada",
                    description: "Los cambios se han guardado correctamente"
                })
            } catch {
                p({
                    title: "Error al guardar",
                    description: "No se pudo guardar la configuración",
                    variant: "destructive"
                })
            } finally {
                x(I => ({
                    ...I,
                    [A]: !1
                }))
            }
        },
        L = (A, P) => {
            b(I => ({
                ...I,
                [A]: P
            }))
        },
        R = async () => {
            x(A => ({
                ...A,
                page: !0
            }));
            try {
                const A = r ? "PUT" : "POST",
                    P = r ? `/api/admin/cms/pages/${r.id}` : "/api/admin/cms/pages";
                if (!(await fetch(P, {
                    method: A,
                    headers: {
                        "Content-Type": "application/json"
                    },
                    credentials: "include",
                    body: JSON.stringify(o)
                })).ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al guardar página");
                v.invalidateQueries({
                    queryKey: ["/api/admin/cms/pages"]
                }),
                n(null),
                l({}),
                m(!1),
                p({
                    title: r ? "Página actualizada" : "Página creada"
                })
            } catch {
                p({
                    title: "Error al guardar página",
                    variant: "destructive"
                })
            } finally {
                x(A => ({
                    ...A,
                    page: !1
                }))
            }
        },
        z = async () => {
            x(A => ({
                ...A,
                block: !0
            }));
            try {
                const A = a ? "PUT" : "POST",
                    P = a ? `/api/admin/cms/footer-blocks/${a.id}` : "/api/admin/cms/footer-blocks";
                if (!(await fetch(P, {
                    method: A,
                    headers: {
                        "Content-Type": "application/json"
                    },
                    credentials: "include",
                    body: JSON.stringify(c)
                })).ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al guardar bloque");
                v.invalidateQueries({
                    queryKey: ["/api/admin/cms/footer-blocks"]
                }),
                i(null),
                d({}),
                y(!1),
                p({
                    title: a ? "Bloque actualizado" : "Bloque creado"
                })
            } catch {
                p({
                    title: "Error al guardar bloque",
                    variant: "destructive"
                })
            } finally {
                x(A => ({
                    ...A,
                    block: !1
                }))
            }
        },
        H = async A => {
            try {
                if (!(await fetch(`/api/admin/cms/footer-blocks/${A}`, {
                    method: "DELETE",
                    credentials: "include"
                })).ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al eliminar bloque");
                v.invalidateQueries({

}

    return e.jsxs(V, {
        className: "w-full max-w-md mx-auto",
        children: [e.jsxs(ae, {
            children: [e.jsx(ie, {
                children: "Pago con Stripe"
            }), e.jsx(qt, {
                children: "Completa tu pago de forma segura"
            })]
        }), e.jsx(U, {
            children: e.jsxs("form", {
                onSubmit: l,
                className: "space-y-4",
                children: [e.jsx(PY, {}), e.jsx(M, {
                    type: "submit",
                    disabled: !r || i,
                    className: "w-full",
                    children: i ? e.jsxs(e.Fragment, {
                        children: [e.jsx(Xt, {
                            className: "mr-2 h-4 w-4 animate-spin"
                        }), "Procesando..."]
                    }) : "Pagar ahora"
                })]
            })
        })]
    })
};
function UY() {
    const [t] = dt(),
        [, s] = Tn(),
        {toast: r} = tt(),
        [n, a] = h.useState(""),
        [i, o] = h.useState(""),
        [l, c] = h.useState("");
    return h.useEffect(() => {
        (async () => {
            try {
                const m = await (await Ie("GET", "/api/payment-modules/stripe/config")).json();
                if (!m.publicKey)
                    throw new Error("Stripe no configurado");
                c(m.publicKey),
                h2 = $Y(m.publicKey);
                const f = new URLSearchParams(t.split("?")[1]),
                    y = f.get("client_secret"),
                    g = f.get("session_id");
                if (!y || !g)
                    throw new Error("Faltan parámetros de pago");
                a(y),
                o(g)
            } catch (u) {
                console.error("Error initializing Stripe:", u),
                r({
                    title: "Error",
                    description: "Error al inicializar Stripe",
                    variant: "destructive"
                }),
                s("/checkout")
            }
        })()
    }, [t, s, r]), n ? e.jsx("div", {
        className: "min-h-screen bg-gray-50 py-12 px-4",
        children: e.jsx("div", {
            className: "max-w-md mx-auto",
            children: e.jsx(QM, {
                stripe: h2,
                options: {
                    clientSecret: n
                },
                children: e.jsx(VY, {
                    clientSecret: n,
                    sessionId: i
                })
            })
        })
    }) : e.jsx("div", {
        className: "min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center",
        children: e.jsx("div", {
            className: "animate-spin w-8 h-8 border-4 border-primary border-t-transparent rounded-full"
        })
    })
}
function qY() {
    const [t] = dt(),
        [, s] = Tn(),
        {toast: r} = tt(),
        [n, a] = h.useState(!0);
    return h.useEffect(() => {
        (async () => {
            try {
                const o = new URLSearchParams(t.split("?")[1]),
                    l = o.get("session_id"),
                    c = o.get("payment_intent");
                if (!l || !c)
                    throw new Error("Missing required parameters");
                const d = JSON.parse(sessionStorage.getItem("pending_order_data") || "{}");
                if (!d.customerEmail)
                    throw new Error("No pending order data found");
                const u = await Ie("POST", "/api/orders/local", {
                    ...d,
                    paymentTransactionId: c,
                    paymentStatus: "completed"
                });
                if (u.ok) {
                    const m = await u.json();
                    sessionStorage.removeItem("pending_order_data"),
                    s(`/order-confirmation/${m.id}?payment=stripe&sessionId=${l}`)
                } else
                    throw new Error("Failed to create order")
            } catch (o) {
                console.error("Error processing payment success:", o),
                r({
                    title: "Error",
                    description: "Hubo un problema al procesar tu pago. Por favor contacta con nosotros.",
                    variant: "destructive"
                }),
                s("/checkout")
            } finally {
                a(!1)
            }
        })()
    }, [t, s, r]), n ? e.jsx("div", {
        className: "min-h-screen bg-gray-50 py-12 px-4",
        children: e.jsx("div", {
            className: "max-w-md mx-auto",
            children: e.jsxs(V, {
                children: [e.jsxs(ae, {
                    children: [e.jsxs(ie, {
                        className: "flex items-center",
                        children: [e.jsx(Xt, {
                            className: "mr-2 h-5 w-5 animate-spin"
                        }), "Procesando pago..."]
                    }), e.jsx(qt, {
                        children: "Estamos confirmando tu pago con Stripe"
                    })]
                }), e.jsx(U, {
                    children: e.jsxs("div", {
                        className: "text-center py-8",
                        children: [e.jsx("div", {
                            className: "animate-spin w-12 h-12 border-4 border-primary border-t-transparent rounded-full mx-auto"
                        }), e.jsx("p", {
                            className: "mt-4 text-gray-600",
                            children: "Por favor, no cierres esta ventana..."
                        })]
                    })
                })]
            })
        })
    }) : e.jsx("div", {
        className: "min-h-screen bg-gray-50 py-12 px-4",
        children: e.jsx("div", {
            className: "max-w-md mx-auto",
            children: e.jsxs(V, {
                children: [e.jsxs(ae, {
                    children: [e.jsxs(ie, {
                        className: "flex items-center text-green-600",
                        children: [e.jsx(It, {
                            className: "mr-2 h-5 w-5"
                        }), "Pago exitoso"]
                    }), e.jsx(qt, {
                        children: "Tu pago ha sido procesado correctamente"
                    })]
                }), e.jsx(U, {
                    children: e.jsx("div", {
                        className: "text-center py-8",
                        children: e.jsx("p", {
                            className: "text-gray-600",
                            children: "Redirigiendo a la confirmación del pedido..."
                        })
                    })
                })]
            })
        })
    })
}
const BY = ({amount: t, sessionId: s}) => {
    const {toast: r} = tt(),
        [, n] = Tn(),
        [a, i] = h.useState(!0),
        o = async () => {
            try {
                const m = await Ie("POST", "/api/paypal/order", {
                    amount: parseFloat(t),
                    currency: "EUR",
                    intent: "CAPTURE"
                });
                if (m.ok)
                    return {
                        orderId: (await m.json()).id
                    };
                throw new Error("Failed to create PayPal order")
            } catch (m) {
                throw console.error("Error creating PayPal order:", m), m
            }
        },
        l = async m => {
            try {
                const f = await Ie("POST", `/api/paypal/order/${m}/capture`);
                if (f.ok)
                    return await f.json();
                throw new Error("Failed to capture PayPal order")
            } catch (f) {
                throw console.error("Error capturing PayPal order:", f), f
            }
        },
        c = async m => {
            try {
                const f = await l(m.orderId);
                if (f.status === "COMPLETED") {
                    const y = JSON.parse(sessionStorage.getItem("pending_order_data") || "{}"),
                        g = await Ie("POST", "/api/orders/local", {
                            ...y,
                            paymentTransactionId: f.id,
                            paymentStatus: "completed"
                        });
                    if (g.ok) {
                        const x = await g.json();
                        sessionStorage.removeItem("pending_order_data"),
                        n(`/order-confirmation/${x.id}?payment=paypal&sessionId=${s}`)
                    }
                }
            } catch {
                r({
                    title: "Error en el pago",
                    description: "Hubo un problema al procesar tu pago con PayPal",
                    variant: "destructive"
                })
            }
        },
        d = () => {
            r({
                title: "Pago cancelado",
                description: "El pago con PayPal fue cancelado",
                variant: "default"
            }),
            n("/checkout")
        },
        u = m => {
            console.error("PayPal error:", m),
            r({
                title: "Error en el pago",
                description: "Hubo un error al procesar el pago con PayPal",
                variant: "destructive"
            })
        };
    return h.useEffect(() => {
        const m = async () => {
                try {
                    if (window.paypal)
                        await f();
                    else {
                        const y = document.createElement("script");
                        y.src = "https://www.paypal.com/web-sdk/v6/core",
                        y.async = !0,
                        y.onload = () => f(),
                        document.body.appendChild(y)
                    }
                } catch (y) {
                    console.error("Failed to load PayPal SDK", y),
                    i(!1)
                }
            },
            f = async () => {
                try {
                    const g = await (await Ie("GET", "/api/paypal/setup")).json(),
                        j = (await window.paypal.createInstance({
                            clientToken: g.clientToken,
                            components: ["paypal-payments"]
                        })).createPayPalOneTimePaymentSession({
                            onApprove: c,
                            onCancel: d,
                            onError: u
                        }),
                        b = async () => {
                            try {
                                const v = o();
                                await j.start({
                                    paymentFlow: "auto"
                                }, v)
                            } catch (v) {
                                console.error("PayPal checkout error:", v),
                                u(v)
                            }
                        },
                        p = document.getElementById("paypal-button");
                    p && p.addEventListener("click", b),
                    i(!1)
                } catch (y) {
                    console.error("PayPal initialization error:", y),
                    i(!1)
                }
            };
        m()
    }, []), a ? e.jsxs("div", {
        className: "flex items-center justify-center py-8",
        children: [e.jsx(Xt, {
            className: "h-8 w-8 animate-spin"
        }), e.jsx("span", {
            className: "ml-2",
            children: "Cargando PayPal..."
        })]
    }) : e.jsxs("div", {
        className: "space-y-4",
        children: [e.jsx("div", {
            className: "text-center",
            children: e.jsxs("p", {
                className: "text-lg font-semibold",
                children: ["Total a pagar: ", t, " €"]
            })
        }), e.jsx("div", {
            className: "flex justify-center",
            children: e.jsx("button", {
                id: "paypal-button",
                className: "bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-3 px-6 rounded-lg transition-colors",
                children: "Pagar con PayPal"
            })
        })]
    })
};
function HY() {
    const [t] = dt(),
        [, s] = Tn(),
        {toast: r} = tt(),
        [n, a] = h.useState(""),
        [i, o] = h.useState("");

        if (!c || !d) {
            r({
                title: "Error",
                description: "Faltan parámetros de pago",

            }),
            s("/checkout");
            return
        }
        a(c),
        o(d)
    }, [t, s, r]), n ? e.jsx("div", {

                                className: "mr-2 h-4 w-4"
                            }), "Volver al checkout"]

            })
        })
    }) : e.jsx("div", {

        children: e.jsx("div", {
            className: "animate-spin w-8 h-8 border-4 border-primary border-t-transparent rounded-full"
        })
    })
}

        delivered: "bg-green-500",

    },
    p2 = {
        pending: "Pendiente",
        processing: "Procesando",
        shipped: "Enviado",
        delivered: "Entregado",
        cancelled: "Cancelado"
    };

        [r, n] = h.useState(null),

        }),

        u = {

            pendingOrders: (a == null ? void 0 : a.filter(m => m.status === "pending").length) || 0,
            totalRevenue: (a == null ? void 0 : a.reduce((m, f) => m + f.totalAmount, 0)) || 0,

}
const KY = ({popup: t, onClose: s, onSuccess: r}) => {
        const {toast: n} = tt(),
            [a, i] = h.useState({
                title: "",
                content: "",
                image: "",
                type: "info",
                position: "center",
                trigger: "immediate",
                triggerValue: 0,
                displayFrequency: "always",
                startDate: "",
                endDate: "",
                isActive: !0,
                priority: 1,
                targetPages: [],
                excludePages: [],
                buttonText: "Cerrar",
                buttonAction: "close",
                buttonUrl: "",
                showCloseButton: !0,
                backdropClose: !0
            }),
            [o, l] = h.useState(""),
            [c, d] = h.useState(""),
            [u, m] = h.useState(null),
            [f, y] = h.useState(""),
            g = v => {
                var w;
                const N = (w = v.target.files) == null ? void 0 : w[0];
                if (N) {
                    if (!N.type.startsWith("image/")) {
                        n({
                            title: "Error",
                            description: "Por favor selecciona un archivo de imagen",
                            variant: "destructive"
                        });
                        return
                    }
                    if (N.size > 5 * 1024 * 1024) {
                        n({
                            title: "Error",
                            description: "La imagen debe ser menor a 5MB",
                            variant: "destructive"
                        });
                        return
                    }
                    m(N);
                    const C = new FileReader;
                    C.onload = E => {
                        var k;
                        y((k = E.target) == null ? void 0 : k.result)
                    },
                    C.readAsDataURL(N)
                }
            };
        h.useEffect(() => {
            t && (i({
                title: t.title,
                content: t.content,
                image: t.image || "",
                type: t.type,
                position: t.position,
                trigger: t.trigger,
                triggerValue: t.triggerValue,
                displayFrequency: t.displayFrequency,
                startDate: t.startDate ? t.startDate.split("T")[0] : "",
                endDate: t.endDate ? t.endDate.split("T")[0] : "",
                isActive: t.isActive,
                priority: t.priority,
                targetPages: t.targetPages || [],
                excludePages: t.excludePages || [],
                buttonText: t.buttonText,
                buttonAction: t.buttonAction,
                buttonUrl: t.buttonUrl || "",
                showCloseButton: t.showCloseButton,
                backdropClose: t.backdropClose
            }), l((t.targetPages || []).join(`
`
            )), d((t.excludePages || []).join(`
`
            )), y(t.image || ""))
        }, [t]);
        const x = async v => {
                const N = new FormData;
                N.append("image", v);
                const w = await fetch("/api/upload/image", {
                    method: "POST",
                    body: N
                });
                if (!w.ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al subir la imagen");
                return (await w.json()).url
            },
            j = rt({
                mutationFn: async v => {
                    const N = t ? `/api/popups/${t.id}` : "/api/popups",
                        C = await fetch(N, {
                            method: t ? "PUT" : "POST",
                            headers: {
                                "Content-Type": "application/json"
                            },
                            body: JSON.stringify(v)
                        });
                    if (!C.ok) {
                        const E = await C.json();
                        throw new Error(E.error || "Error al guardar el pop-up")
                    }
                    return C.json()
                },
                onSuccess: () => {
                    n({
                        title: "Éxito",
                        description: `Pop-up ${t ? "actualizado" : "creado"} correctamente`
                    }),
                    r()
                },
                onError: v => {
                    n({
                        title: "Error",
                        description: v.message,
                        variant: "destructive"
                    })
                }
            }),
            b = async v => {
                if (v.preventDefault(), !a.title.trim()) {
                    n({
                        title: "Error",
                        description: "El título es obligatorio",
                        variant: "destructive"
                    });
                    return
                }
                if (!a.content.trim()) {
                    n({
                        title: "Error",
                        description: "El contenido es obligatorio",
                        variant: "destructive"
                    });
                    return
                }
                try {
                    let N = a.image;
                    u && (N = await x(u));
                    const w = o.trim() ? o.split(`
`
                        ).map(k => k.trim()).filter(k => k.length > 0) : [],
                        C = c.trim() ? c.split(`
`
                        ).map(k => k.trim()).filter(k => k.length > 0) : [],
                        E = {
                            ...a,
                            image: N,
                            targetPages: w.length > 0 ? w : null,
                            excludePages: C.length > 0 ? C : null,
                            startDate: a.startDate ? new Date(a.startDate).toISOString() : null,
                            endDate: a.endDate ? new Date(a.endDate).toISOString() : null
                        };
                    j.mutate(E)
                } catch {
                    n({
                        title: "Error",
                        description: "Error al subir la imagen",
                        variant: "destructive"
                    })
                }
            },
            p = (v, N) => {
                i(w => ({
                    ...w,
                    [v]: N
                }))
            };
        return e.jsx("div", {
            className: "fixed inset-0 z-50 bg-black bg-opacity-50 flex items-center justify-center p-4",
            children: e.jsxs("div", {
                className: "bg-white rounded-lg shadow-xl max-w-4xl w-full max-h-[90vh] overflow-y-auto",
                children: [e.jsxs("div", {
                    className: "sticky top-0 bg-white border-b px-6 py-4 flex justify-between items-center",
                    children: [e.jsx("h2", {
                        className: "text-xl font-semibold",
                        children: t ? "Editar Pop-up" : "Nuevo Pop-up"
                    }), e.jsx(M, {
                        variant: "ghost",
                        size: "sm",
                        onClick: s,
                        children: e.jsx(er, {
                            className: "h-4 w-4"
                        })
                    })]
                }), e.jsxs("form", {
                    onSubmit: b,
                    className: "p-6",
                    children: [e.jsxs(ls, {
                        defaultValue: "basic",
                        className: "space-y-6",
                        children: [e.jsxs(es, {
                            className: "grid w-full grid-cols-4",
                            children: [e.jsx(Ve, {
                                value: "basic",
                                children: "Básico"
                            }), e.jsx(Ve, {
                                value: "behavior",
                                children: "Comportamiento"
                            }), e.jsx(Ve, {
                                value: "targeting",
                                children: "Segmentación"
                            }), e.jsx(Ve, {
                                value: "advanced",
                                children: "Avanzado"
                            })]
                        }), e.jsx(ze, {
                            value: "basic",
                            className: "space-y-4",
                            children: e.jsxs(V, {
                                children: [e.jsx(ae, {
                                    children: e.jsxs(ie, {
                                        className: "flex items-center gap-2",
                                        children: [e.jsx(Bs, {
                                            className: "h-5 w-5"
                                        }), "Información Básica"]
                                    })
                                }), e.jsxs(U, {
                                    className: "space-y-4",
                                    children: [e.jsxs("div", {
                                        children: [e.jsx(q, {
                                            htmlFor: "title",
                                            children: "Título *"
                                        }), e.jsx(se, {
                                            id: "title",
                                            value: a.title,
                                            onChange: v => p("title", v.target.value),
                                            placeholder: "Título del pop-up",
                                            required: !0
                                        })]
                                    }), e.jsxs("div", {
                                        children: [e.jsx(q, {
                                            htmlFor: "content",
                                            children: "Contenido * (HTML permitido)"
                                        }), e.jsx(Ut, {
                                            id: "content",
                                            value: a.content,
                                            onChange: v => p("content", v.target.value),
                                            placeholder: "Contenido del pop-up. Puedes usar HTML básico como <b>, <i>, <a>, etc.",
                                            rows: 6,
                                            required: !0
                                        })]
                                    }), e.jsxs("div", {
                                        children: [e.jsx(q, {
                                            htmlFor: "image",
                                            children: "Imagen (opcional)"
                                        }), e.jsxs("div", {
                                            className: "space-y-2",
                                            children: [e.jsxs("div", {
                                                className: "flex items-center gap-2",
                                                children: [e.jsx("input", {
                                                    type: "file",
                                                    id: "image",
                                                    accept: "image/*",
                                                    onChange: g,
                                                    className: "hidden"
                                                }), e.jsxs(M, {
                                                    type: "button",
                                                    variant: "outline",
                                                    onClick: () => {
                                                        var v;
                                                        return (v = document.getElementById("image")) == null ? void 0 : v.click()
                                                    },
                                                    className: "flex items-center gap-2",
                                                    children: [e.jsx(ci, {
                                                        className: "h-4 w-4"
                                                    }), "Subir imagen"]
                                                }), f && e.jsx(M, {
                                                    type: "button",
                                                    variant: "outline",
                                                    size: "sm",
                                                    onClick: () => {
                                                        y(""),
                                                        m(null),
                                                        i(v => ({
                                                            ...v,
                                                            image: ""
                                                        }))
                                                    },
                                                    children: e.jsx(er, {
                                                        className: "h-4 w-4"
                                                    })
                                                })]
                                            }), f && e.jsx("div", {
                                                className: "border rounded-lg p-2",
                                                children: e.jsx("img", {
                                                    src: f,
                                                    alt: "Preview",
                                                    className: "max-w-full max-h-32 object-contain rounded"
                                                })
                                            }), e.jsx("p", {
                                                className: "text-sm text-gray-500",
                                                children: "Formatos soportados: JPEG, PNG, GIF. Tamaño máximo: 5MB"
                                            })]
                                        })]
                                    }), e.jsxs("div", {
                                        className: "grid grid-cols-2 gap-4",
                                        children: [e.jsxs("div", {
                                            children: [e.jsx(q, {
                                                htmlFor: "type",
                                                children: "Tipo"
                                            }), e.jsxs(He, {
                                                value: a.type,
                                                onValueChange: v => p("type", v),
                                                children: [e.jsx(Ue, {
                                                    children: e.jsx(We, {})
                                                }), e.jsxs(qe, {
                                                    children: [e.jsx(Q, {
                                                        value: "info",
                                                        children: "Información"
                                                    }), e.jsx(Q, {
                                                        value: "warning",
                                                        children: "Advertencia"
                                                    }), e.jsx(Q, {
                                                        value: "promotion",

    YY = ({popupId: t, onClose: s}) => {
        const {data: r, isLoading: n} = _e({
            queryKey: [`/api/popups/${t}/stats`],
            queryFn: async () => {
                const o = await fetch(`/api/popups/${t}/stats`);
                if (!o.ok)
                    throw new Error("Error al obtener estadísticas");
                return o.json()
            }
        });
        if (n)
            return e.jsx("div", {
                className: "fixed inset-0 z-50 bg-black bg-opacity-50 flex items-center justify-center",
                children: e.jsxs("div", {

                    }), e.jsx("p", {
                        className: "mt-2 text-gray-600",
                        children: "Cargando estadísticas..."
                    })]
                })
            });
        const {summary: a={}, stats: i=[]} = r || {};
        return e.jsx("div", {
            className: "fixed inset-0 z-50 bg-black bg-opacity-50 flex items-center justify-center p-4",

                                })]
                            })

                                    className: "text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900",
                                    children: a.totalClicks || 0
                                }), e.jsx("div", {

                                })]
                            })

                                    className: "text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900",

                            })
                        }), e.jsx(V, {

                                    children: a.clickRate ? `${a.clickRate.toFixed(1)}%` : "0%"
                                }), e.jsx("div", {
                                    className: "text-sm text-gray-600",

                                })]

                        })]

                        children: [e.jsx(ae, {
